source:
TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
Rhil Ril has stumbled upon something rather intriguing.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête
Rhil Ril a les yeux qui brillent en vous regardant.

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_TODO_00<tab>Use the rusty spade to dig at the designated location.
TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the rotted chest to Rhil Ril and return his rusty spade.
TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_000<tab>You must be a traveler, yes? Then maybe you can help me.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_000<tab>Salut à toi, humain<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>! J'ai quelque chose de très intéressant à partager avec toi, si ça t'intéresse, voui. Tu veux savoir quoi, le veux-tu<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_001<tab>I was looking around an abandoned house and I found a map of Amh Araeng, with a big cross drawn on it. It can only mean one thing─treasure!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_001<tab>Eh bien, en faisant du rangement dans une maison abandonnée, j'ai trouvé un dessin des environs avec un étrange sceau dessus, voui. C'est peut-être une carte au trésor, une carte au trésor<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_002<tab>I want to go and look for it, but I have to stay here and guard the village. Could you go in my stead?
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_002<tab>Mal<var 16 /var>heu<var 16 /var>reu<var 16 /var>se<var 16 /var>ment, je peux pas quitter mon poste parce que je dois faire le guet ici, je peux pas... Mais toi, tu pourrais aller chercher le trésor, oui<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_003<tab>If there are any shinies to be had, we can share them, yes? Here, take my spade and dig where the cross is!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_003<tab>Et s'il y en a bien un, on pourrait se le partager<var 1D /var>! Tiens, je te prête mon matériel. Tu n'as qu'à aller creuser à l'endroit indiqué sur la carte, voui, va creuser là-bas<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_010<tab>Be sure to bring the treasure to me, along with my spade! You do not want to know what happens to thieves around here...
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_010<tab>Si tu vas creuser à l'endroit indiqué sur la carte avec le matériel que je t'ai prêté, tu trouveras peut-être un trésor, et on se le partagera, voui, on va se le partager<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>You discover a rotted chest buried in the soil.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>En creusant, vous avez découvert <var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E8EDB0202 /var> dans le sol<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_030<tab>Show me what you found! Show me! And give me my spade back, please!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_030<tab>Te revoilà<var 1D /var>! Tu as trouvé quelque chose, voui<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_031<tab>Oh, this must be very old... Let us see what is inside...
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_031<tab>Voooh<var 1D /var>! Il y avait donc un coffre enfoui à cet endroit, voui<var 1D /var>! Vite, il faut l'ouvrir<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_032<tab>What!? Nothing but junk! Rusty junk, at that! Why would anyone bury this? Wait, is that a diary? I am sure the former owner will not mind if I take a peek...
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_032<tab>... Vmmm... Il y a que des bricoles sans valeur, voui, sans valeur. Tiens, on dirait un journal, ça...

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_033<tab>Hmm... It looks like the owner had to leave Amh Araeng but was planning to come back one day.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_033<tab>Voyons, voyons... “Je suis triste de quitter Amh Araeng, mais un jour, je reviendrai”...

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_034<tab>And if that day ever came, they wanted to dig up the diary and continue writing their life story.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_034<tab>“Et ce jour-là, je relirai mon journal et je continuerai de l'écrire”...

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_035<tab>I wonder if that person is still alive... Probably not, judging by the state of this chest. It must have been buried for a long time. Maybe their children, or their children's children will come in search of it.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_035<tab>Vmmm... Si la vie reprend en Amh Araeng, l'humain qui a écrit ça rentrera sûrement, voui, sûrement. Si c'est pas lui, ça sera ses enfants ou ses petits-enfants...

source: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_036<tab>If I read the rest, maybe I can learn who this person was... And then I will put it back, in a more sturdy box. And since there was no treasure to share, I will give you this instead as payment for your hard work!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG004_03489_RHILRIL_000_036<tab>Je vais conserver le journal et <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8EDB0202 /var> jusqu'à ce que ce jour arrive. Merci, humain<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>, voui, merci à toi<var 1D /var>! Tiens, voilà une petite récompense, une récompense<var 1D /var>!
